data.description: Back on market, buyer financing fell through! Appraised at value! This beautiful corner lot home sits on a .21 acre lot! Possible multigenerational home with full bedroom on 1st floor! As you walk in you are greeted w/ a nice open concept. Great flex room can be formal dining room, 2nd living room, or office, the possibilities are endless! Kitchen cabinets were recently professionally painted. Living room is open to kitchen which is great for entertaining. Wood-like ceramic tile all through the 1st floor. Upstairs has the rest of the 4 bedrooms and loft area that can be easily be converted to bedroom if needed! Master bedroom suite is very spacious and the closet has room for all your needs. Yard is huge, patio recently extended and sun setter awning installed which makes the perfect backyard oasis. Ask about preferred lender incentives!
